OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FProlonged
OL,6,Fsunny spells for most to end the day.
OL,7,FA fine and dry night with mostly clear
OL,8,Fskies across the region. Some fog
OL,9,Fpatches may form later but will remain
OL,10,Fisolated. Winds staying light. Feeling
OL,11,Fwarm overnight for some.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother bright and sunny
OL,14,Fday, the sunshine may turn a little
OL,15,Fhazy due to high-level cloud later on.
OL,16,FTurning hot or very hot by the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Winds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
