OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry,
OL,6,Fsunny and hot throughout. Cloud
OL,7,Fforming overnight with onshore flow,
OL,8,Fbut is expected quickly burn back
OL,9,Fduring the day. A freshening north-
OL,10,Feasterly wind developing Saturday.
OL,11,FTemperatures well above average.
